_sText:
Hello all,

Tiny little update on de_westwood. I hear tons of people complaining about the annoying fog/dust. I removed it and now the map is much much better. 

As I didnot have the textures I had to remake the textures for this map. They are slightly different but it's fine.

All the honor goes to the mapmaker : cc_nipper. You can comment on his map in the link below:

http://www.gamebanana.com/maps/12691

Have fun and play fair!

ps; If you want to have bots on this map. Dowload the .nav from the original de_westwood (see link above) and rename .nav to de_westwood_no_fog. Voila, you've got your bots.
